messages.text: Hello, this is Michael from City Pharma. I'm calling to follow up on order number PO-2025-1147. Can you provide an update on the delivery status?
Hello Michael. Let me check that order for you. One moment please.
I found it. Order PO-2025-1147 was shipped yesterday and is currently in transit. It should arrive at your location by tomorrow afternoon, November 17th.
That's wonderful news. Can you provide a tracking number so we can monitor the shipment?
Yes, the tracking number is TRK-789456123. You can track it on our website or through the carrier's system.
Perfect, I've noted the tracking number. Is there anything else we should be aware of regarding this delivery?
No, everything looks good. The order is complete and on schedule. If you have any issues upon delivery, please don't hesitate to contact us.
Thank you very much for the update. We appreciate your prompt response. Have a great day!
You're welcome, Michael. Have a great day as well. Goodbye!
